Google Search Scraper | LeadStal

🔍 Google Search Scraper & Email Finder is a fast and efficient Chrome extension by LeadStal that empowers you to extract business leads directly from Google search results. This tool is designed for quick and seamless lead generation, allowing you to collect relevant contact details effortlessly.

Simple Signup & Start Collecting Leads
Install the Extension: Add Google Search Scraper to your Chrome browser.
Quick Signup: Sign up instantly using your Google email.
Search for Leads: Input what you're searching for (e.g., "digital marketing agency" or "plumbing services") in Google’s search bar.
Generate Leads: Click the Generate Leads button, and the tool will begin extracting lead data automatically.


Key Features:
📊 Smart Lead Collection: Extract comprehensive leads, including all details from Google search.
💡 Credit-Efficient System: You only pay for valid leads, making it cost-effective.
⚡ Real-Time Syncing: View collected leads immediately, with a clean, synchronized display.
✅ User-Friendly Interface: Easy to navigate for users of all levels.
🔐 Data Security: Secure handling of all data, ensuring privacy and safety.

Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ):
❓ How do I get started with Google Search Scraper?
Simply install the extension, sign up with your Google email, and start generating leads by entering relevant search terms into Google.
📝 What data does the extension collect?
Google Search Scraper collects titles, phone numbers, emails, websites, and social media profiles from Google search results.
💰 Is there a free trial available?
Yes, the extension offers a free trial with limited credits. Once the trial ends, you can purchase more credits for continued usage.
🎯 How does the credit system work?
You only use credits for valid leads. Invalid or incomplete data is excluded, ensuring efficient credit usage.
📂 Can I export the collected leads?
Yes, all collected leads can be exported for further use in your CRM or other tools.
🖥️ Which browsers support Google Search Scraper?
Currently, Google Search Scraper is available exclusively for Chrome. Support for other browsers may be added in the future. 
🔄 How frequently is the data updated?
The data is scraped in real-time from live Google search results, ensuring the most up-to-date leads.
🔒 How secure is my information?
Your data is encrypted and handled with top-tier security measures to ensure privacy and protection.
🔄 Can I use this tool for multiple types of businesses?
Yes, the tool works for a variety of industries, including digital marketing, plumbing, software companies, and more.
🛠️ What if I encounter an issue with the extension?
LeadStal provides dedicated customer support to assist you with any issues you may face.


💡 Get Started Today with Google Search Scraper and start collecting valuable leads from Google search in just a few clicks!
